<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>人物介绍 - 薄昕炎</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .profile-img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            background: url('boxinyan.png') center/cover no-repeat;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .age {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        section {
            padding: 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #2575fc;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f4f8;
        }
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 30px;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .timeline:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 10px;
            height: 90%;
            width: 3px;
            background: #6a11cb;
        }
        .timeline-item {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .timeline-item:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -33px;
            top: 5px;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #2575fc;
            border: 3px solid #6a11cb;
        }
        .timeline-year {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #6a11cb;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: #666;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header {
                padding: 30px 15px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            section {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="profile-img"></div>
            <h1>薄昕炎</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">"量子计算先锋"</div>
            <div class="age">32岁</div>
        </header>

        <section id="early-life">
            <h2>早年经历</h2>
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-year">1995-2001</div>
                    <p>空白</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-year">2002</div>
                    <p>空白</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-year">2003-2006</div>
                    <p>空白</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="education">
            <h2>教育背景</h2>
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-year">2007-2011</div>
                    <p><strong>佳木斯大学</strong> · 本科生</p>
                    <p>师从著名量子物理学家陈教授，大三时在《Physical Review Letters》发表关于量子退相干抑制的论文。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-year">2011-2016</div>
                    <p><strong>麻省理工学院</strong> · 量子计算博士</p>
                    <p>开发出"Li-Qubit"量子比特稳定技术，突破量子计算机持续运算时间纪录，获IEEE最佳博士论文奖。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="honors">
            <h2>荣誉与美称</h2>
            <ul style="list-style: none;">
                <li style="padding: 10px; background: #f0f7ff; margin-bottom: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #6a11cb;">
                    <strong>"量子计算先锋"</strong> - 因突破性量子门设计获《Nature》2018年度十大科学人物称号
                </li>
                <li style="padding: 10px; background: #f0f7ff; margin-bottom: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #2575fc;">
                    <strong>"中国青年科学家奖"</strong> - 2020年因量子算法研究获得国家级科技表彰
                </li>
                <li style="padding: 10px; background: #f0f7ff; margin-bottom: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #6a11cb;">
                    <strong>IEEE Medal of Honor</strong> - 史上最年轻获得者（2023年）
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>© 2025 李思远人物档案 | 设计参考：HTML5个人模板[1,5](@ref)</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
